1. Error-handling middleware + process-level handlers (prevents crashes and leaks).
2. `helmet` + body-size limit (one-line wins, big defense-in-depth payoff).
3. Validation library before you add any route that takes input.
4. Rate limiting + structured logging.
5. Graceful shutdown + configurable port.

