app.use(rateLimit({ windowMs: 60_000, max: 100 })); // basic DoS protection
```

### 2. Validate and sanitize input

Even though current endpoints take no parameters, any future additions should validate at the boundary. Use a schema validator rather than ad-hoc checks:

```js
const { z } = require('zod');

const UserIdSchema = z.object({ id: z.coerce.number().int().positive() });

