- Validate required env vars at startup (fail fast) using zod or envalid.
- Never commit secrets; load via `.env` + a secret manager in prod.

### 6. Graceful shutdown and process-level errors

```js
const server = app.listen(port, () => { /* ... */ });

process.on('unhandledRejection', (reason) => { /* log + exit */ });
process.on('uncaughtException', (err) => { /* log + exit */ });
process.on('SIGTERM', () => server.close(() => process.exit(0)));
```

Without this, an unhandled rejection leaves the process in an undefined state — a known security/reliability risk.

